{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_01_02",
  "title": "伝えるなら\n一緒に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんとお姉ちゃんも{user}さんに\n内緒でライブを計画していたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san and you‚\nwere you planning a secret live for {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ。だからサニピと月ストのみんなが\n感謝のライブがしたいって言い出した時は驚いちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's right. So when Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest\nsaid they wanted to do a gratitude live‚ I was surprised",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6561682701,
      "endTime": 14.9641724587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あの時の私達と同じだったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "because it reminded me of our situation back then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1561682701,
      "endTime": 18.022494173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "それで麻奈さんとのライブはどうなったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about the live with Mana-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.2228344281,
      "endTime": 21.6167799313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんが誘ってくれたのは嬉しかったけど……\nやっぱり自信がなくて、ちゃんと断ろうと思ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was happy that she invited me‚ but…\nI still lacked confidence‚ so I was thinking of properly declining it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8228344281,
      "endTime": 29.8106348355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.0728344281
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……。麻奈ちゃんと一緒に歌うなんて\nやっぱり私には無理よ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… Singing with Mana-chan…\nI'm just not cut out for it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1228344281,
      "endTime": 39.8848753292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.0895010948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "知名度も実力もない私と歌うより、麻奈ちゃんが一人で\nライブした方がいいに決まってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather than singing with someone like me who has no fame or talent‚\nit's better if Mana-chan does the live alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0895010948,
      "endTime": 47.588344574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.7895010948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_tired-01.m4a",
      "text": "はーるーこーちゃんっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haaaruuukooo-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7895010948,
      "endTime": 50.4333312988,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 199.99999999999574
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7561644553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、麻奈ちゃん！？　どうして学校に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ Mana-chan!? Why are you at school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7561644553,
      "endTime": 54.5539421557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7561644553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "メッセしてるのに全然返事くれないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since you didn't respond to my messages at all‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7561644553,
      "endTime": 58.166668001800005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-08.m4a",
      "text": "私の方から会いに来ちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I decided to come see you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1666680018,
      "endTime": 61.133334668399996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この間の話の続きだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About what we talked about the other day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.4895018577,
      "endTime": 64.0936863372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0936863372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-03.m4a",
      "text": "ライブで私と一緒に歌ってくれるよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will you sing with me at the live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0936863372,
      "endTime": 67.4333316166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.78949728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "誘ってくれるのは嬉しいけど……\n私じゃ麻奈ちゃんの相手は務まらないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm happy you invited me‚ but…\nI don't think I can match up to you‚ Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.78949728,
      "endTime": 74.43809146870001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "だから、ライブでは私の分まで\n麻奈ちゃんが歌ってちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ at the live‚ please sing not just your part‚\nbut mine too‚ Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.6228306133,
      "endTime": 78.9995880443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.18949728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、ライブのお手伝いはするわ\n今回は裏方として麻奈ちゃんを支えるから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I'll help with the live\nfrom behind the scenes this time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.18949728,
      "endTime": 85.1134882926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.3228306133
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんと{user}君が感動するような\nいいライブにしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's make it a good live that Saegusa-san and\n{user} will be moved by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3228306133,
      "endTime": 89.8666636149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.1228351909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遙子ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1228351909,
      "endTime": 92.20000133500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.5561619121
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さん達には感謝してるし）\n（私も歌いたい気持ちはある……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm grateful to Saegusa-san and manager‚ and）\n（I do want to sing too…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5561619121,
      "endTime": 98.0352094966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2228285788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、私が麻奈ちゃんと並んで歌うなんて）\n（やっぱりふさわしくないわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But‚ me singing alongside Mana-chan…）\n（It just doesn't seem right.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2228285788,
      "endTime": 104.94600296009999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈ちゃんが一人で歌った方が絶対にいいものになる）\n（だから、これで良かったのよ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana-chan singing alone will definitely be better.）\n（So‚ this is for the best…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1561619121,
      "endTime": 112.8295859653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0228285788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-05.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、遙子ちゃん。少しお散歩しない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Haruko-chan. Want to take a little walk?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.0228285788,
      "endTime": 117.7000018436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、今から？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9895033836,
      "endTime": 120.2181655645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.4228367169
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4228367169,
      "endTime": 122.1666685103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-26.m4a",
      "text": "それとも、遙子ちゃんは私と一緒に歩くのは嫌？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or maybe you don't want to walk with me‚ Haruko-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1666685103,
      "endTime": 126.997503503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
