      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人でアイスを食べながら帰ったの覚えてる？",
      "translations": {
