      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-09.m4a",
      "text": "一人ぼっちだと思ったことはなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never felt alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.4142900785,
      "endTime": 273.73331076290003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遙子ちゃんがいてくれて心強かったし、遙子ちゃんに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having you by my side was reassuring‚ and I always felt like",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.0560947736,
      "endTime": 278.2341839154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "負けないように頑張らなきゃっていつも思ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had to do my best so as not to lose to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.2341839154,
      "endTime": 282.3640989621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "遙子ちゃんが居てくれたから、私は沢山頑張れたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you were there‚ I was able to do my best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 282.5560947736,
      "endTime": 287.86666444120004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "……私も同じよ\n麻奈ちゃんがいたから私も諦めずに頑張れた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I feel the same way.\nBecause you were there‚ I was able to keep pushing forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 288.2894626935,
      "endTime": 294.7956756909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達は同じ星見プロの仲間で、大事な友達で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As a teammate from Hoshimi Prods‚ and as important friends‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 295.0561130841,
      "endTime": 299.7560947736,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "励まし合ってずっと一緒に頑張ってきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "we've always supported each other and worked hard together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.7666461307,
      "endTime": 303.5640989621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから三枝さん達に感謝を伝える時は、遙子ちゃんと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why when we express our gratitude to Saegusa-san and the others‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 303.7560947736,
      "endTime": 308.0453006088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-14.m4a",
      "text": "一緒がいいの。遙子ちゃんと一緒じゃなきゃ嫌なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it's better to do it together‚ Haruko-chan. I don't want to do it alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.4561069806,
      "endTime": 312.26411116910003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "遙子ちゃん、私と歌おう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-chan‚ let's sing together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 312.4561069806,
      "endTime": 315.27958609899997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-15.m4a",
      "text": "二人でみんなに感謝を伝えよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's express our gratitude to everyone together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.279586099,
      "endTime": 318.6640745481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "……ずるいわ\nそんな風に言われたら、断れる訳ないじゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're being unfair.\nWhen you put it like that‚ I can't refuse…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 318.8560703595,
      "endTime": 324.6383835157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "……今回だけだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But just this once‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 324.8227370262,
      "endTime": 326.9333155313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "次に一緒にステージに立つ時は、私が麻奈ちゃんに\n負けないくらい人気のアイドルになった時だからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next time we stand on stage together will be\nwhen I've become as popular as you‚ Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 327.156076463,
      "endTime": 334.9162576992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-10.m4a",
      "text": "うん……いつか二人でステージに立とうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Let's stand on stage together someday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.1227431297,
      "endTime": 338.9666583377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その日が来るのを待ってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be waiting for that day to come.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 338.9666583377,
      "endTime": 341.8999916711,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_02-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "待っててね。いつか必ず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be waiting. It will surely come someday…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.1560988426,
      "endTime": 345.46725540159997,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}